set_name

public void set_name(java.lang.String name)
              throws java.lang.Exception
 The name of the load balancing server. If no load balancing virtual server name is entered, a list of all configured load balancing virtual servers is displayed.
All the services and priority queuing/SureConnect  policies that are bound to this virtual server are also displayed.
 Minimum length =  1
